Text-FixEOL version 1.00
========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Alternatively, if you have Module::Build installed, you can build
by typing the following (this method does not depend on having
'make' installed):

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More       (0.54 or later)
  Test::NoWarnings (0.07 or later)
  Test::Pod        (1.20 or later)

They are only used during testing of the build.

